items: Innovative, thoughtful, and integration-minded engineering leader with 10+ years in FE, specializing in search engineering. Proven track record of bridging product, data, and engineering through strong cross-functional collaboration. Passionate about evolving with the product journey, applying deep expertise in A/B testing, metrics-driven optimization, and product launches. Creative thinking and problem-solving are core strengths, demonstrated by multiple world-class hackathon prizes and academic awards. Years of Muay Thai experience have cultivated optimism, adaptability, and crisis management skills under high pressure.
